text: Kennedy Noble is an American swimmer. She won gold medals in 200 metres backstroke, and Mixed 4x100 metres Medley Relay, at the 2023 Pan American Games. == Career == She swam for Millennium High School. She won the 100 metres backstroke at the 2019 Junior Nationals. She competed at the 2021 FINA Swimming World Cup.
